description:
Completed Study Sessions 7 and 8, but looking for more question practice?

Fitch Learning's Workshops are short sessions designed to cover the trickiest topics. In these recordings, our expert tutors will walk you through a selection of exam-standard questions.

Visit the Fitch Learning page to enrol for the following workshops at just $20 each.

- Workshop 1: Ethics and Quantitative Methods (Study Sessions 1 & 2)
- Workshop 2: Financial Reporting and Analysis I (Study Sessions 7 & 8)
- Workshop 3: Financial Reporting and Analysis II (Study Sessions 8, 9 & 10)
- Workshop 4: Fixed Income and Equity (Study Sessions 13, 14, 15 and 16)
- Workshop 5: Corporate Finance, Quantitative Methods II, and Derivatives (Study Sessions 3, 11 & 17)
- Workshop 6: Alternative Investments, Portfolio Management, and Economics (Study Sessions 18, 12, 4, 5 and 6)


This course relates to the 2014 Level I curriculum.
title: CFA Level I Workshop 2: Financial Reporting & Analysis I
